{"tid":1988993,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"日軍屠殺中國人 都係有高尚情操！","createTime":"2020-04-25T14:55:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-26T09:31:17.000Z","uid":222970,"like":238,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"dfeedb57c17784abefc2af7396af86aa2ac6af5a","tid":1988993,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T14:55:49.000Z","msg":"<strong><br />\n中國人抗日時期儼如一支軍隊，更作出「文革式」的極端行為。日軍遭中國人的霸凌行為被弄的奄奄一息、滿身鮮血。<br />\n<br />\n日軍並非有預謀帶刀傷人，日軍因中國霸凌行為的壓力下一時情緒失控，他因此導致「滿身鮮血，奄奄一息」，他只是反常態地「發出最後一聲咆哮」，加上日軍須回國照顧家人<br />\n<br />\n日軍的行為歸咎中國的霸凌行為實屬合理，又讚揚日軍願意接受懲罰，情操高崇，更謂「這情操在一些接受高等教育的知識分子及專業人士身上都沒有」。<br />\n</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dH5NMOE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdH5NMOE.jpg&h=24e7099e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dfb55d8e891611d237d161178d6cd9966a9de12c","tid":1988993,"uid":109345,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T14:57:09.000Z","msg":"總編輯認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd1a280b87d9b6d3d5d44062414c565eae26016c","tid":1988993,"uid":33874,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T14:57:57.000Z","msg":"垃圾日本仔<br />\n當年殺乾淨啲而家咪唔洗煩"},{"pid":"f317c3267a5900a964fbe67336f214be9df1dd24","tid":1988993,"uid":181092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T14:58:49.000Z","msg":"POST去大陸"},{"pid":"7225c666b7269d692fd71bb60e488d7881dac5b9","tid":1988993,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T15:00:32.000Z","msg":"老一認同"},{"pid":"5c3798eeeecf8ca7f79412312bbeaffd0711a32e","tid":1988993,"uid":222970,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f317c3267a5900a964fbe67336f214be9df1dd24","tid":1988993,"uid":181092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T14:58:49.000Z","msg":"POST去大陸"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T15:01:09.000Z","msg":"要Post 埋個狗官講嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n中國人喺微博未必知道呢單新聞"},{"pid":"553aab6ec0a28ee